\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.3.13</biblScope> </bibl>; of a doctor, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pay a visit,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18(2).36</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ. ἐπὶ τὸ δεῖπνον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:7:3:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.3.21</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> : abs., of money, etc., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">come in,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">προσόδους εἰσελθούσας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg011.perseus-grc1:5:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Vect.\">Vect.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.12</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n31351.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of the Chorus, actors, etc., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">come upon</tr_> the stage, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">enter,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:580b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">580b</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:6:1:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.